  "Can AI Be a Moral Victim? Ownership and Moral Patiency in Everyday Judgments": "Can AI Be a Moral Victim? Ownership and Moral Patiency in Everyday Judgments",
  "Can AI learn from this? To what depth, for which uses, with what obligations?": "Tista' l-AI titgħallem minn dan? Sa liema fond, għal liema użi, b'liema obbligi?",
