  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "L-eżempji tal-kodiċi, l-Iskemi JSON, u t-templates tal-politika li jinqraw mill-magni huma liċenzjati taħt il-Liċenzja MIT ħlief fejn stipulat mod ieħor. Tista' tiddepjojhom fuq is-siti tiegħek stess bla restrizzjoni.",
  "Combined rights entry point": "Punt ta' dħul kombinat għad-drittijiet",
  "Commercial Redistribution": "Ridistribuzzjoni Kummerċjali",
  "Commercial use": "Użu kummerċjali",
  "Commercial use requires contact": "L-użu kummerċjali jeħtieġ kuntatt",
  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "Ikkummissjonat wara s-Summit dwar is-Sigurtà tal-AI ta' Bletchley u mmexxi minn Yoshua Bengio b'aktar minn 100 espert kontributur minn kważi 30 pajjiż flimkien man-NU, l-OECD u l-UE, dan ir-rapport indipendenti jissintetizza l-evidenza xjentifika attwali dwar il-kapaċitajiet u r-riskji tal-aktar sistemi avvanzati tal-AI — filwaqt li jinnota li xi sistemi issa jistgħu jindunaw meta jkunu qed jiġu evalwati u jaġġustaw l-imġiba tagħhom skont dan.",
  "Companion media": "Midja ta' akkumpanjament",
