  "Verified in both LTR and RTL contexts: the panel mirrors correctly for Arabic and Persian without any special-casing, using logical CSS positioning.": "Ivverifikat kemm f'kuntesti LTR kif ukoll RTL: il-pannell jimmirja korrettament għall-Għarbi u l-Persjan mingħajr l-ebda trattament speċjali, permezz tal-użu ta' pożizzjonar loġiku tas-CSS.",
  "Verify": "Ivverifika",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts.": "L-istorja tal-verżjonijiet ta' dan is-sit u l-abbozzi tal-protokoll tiegħu.",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts. Breaking spec changes are recorded here.": "L-istorja tal-verżjonijiet ta' dan is-sit u l-abbozzi tal-protokoll tiegħu. Il-bidliet fl-ispeċifikazzjoni li jiksru l-kompatibbiltà huma rreġistrati hawnhekk.",
  "Versioned specifications, JSON Schemas, and the policy files actually deployed on this site. Every file can be downloaded, validated, and cited directly.": "Speċifikazzjonijiet ivverżjonati, JSON Schemas, u l-fajls tal-politika li huma effettivament użati fuq dan is-sit. Kull fajl jista' jitniżżel, jiġi vvalidat, u jiġi ċċitat direttament.",
  "Versioning": "Ivverżjonar",
  "Versions": "Verżjonijiet",
  "Video and audio companions to the protocols and papers — the AI rights layer, watchable and listenable.": "Materjal video u awdjo li jakkumpanja l-protokolli u d-dokumenti — is-saff tad-drittijiet tal-AI, li jista' jitħares u jinstema'.",
  "Videos": "Vidjows",
  "Want to generate your own policy file?": "Trid tiġġenera l-fajl tal-politika tiegħek stess?",
  "Web fonts are loaded from Google Fonts, which receives standard font requests from your browser. No other third-party scripts are used.": "It-tipi ta' ittri tal-web jitgħabbew minn Google Fonts, li tirċievi talbiet standard għat-tipi ta' ittri mill-browser tiegħek. Ma jintużaw l-ebda scripts oħra ta' partijiet terzi.",
  "What AI systems may do with content: read, summarize, transform, retrieve, train, commercialize, redistribute. The AICR ruleset and the AICL licensing layer make these rights declarable and transactable.": "X'jistgħu jagħmlu s-sistemi tal-AI bil-kontenut: jaqrawh, jiġbruh fil-qosor, jittrasformawh, jirkuprawh, jitħarrġu fuqu, jikkummerċjalizzawh, jerġgħu jqassmuh. Is-sett ta' regoli AICR u s-saff ta' liċenzjar AICL jagħmlu dawn id-drittijiet dikjarabbli u negozjabbli.",
  "What a server can return when an AI crawler requests licensed content without a license token — a machine-actionable quote instead of a dead end.": "X'jista' jirritorna server meta crawler tal-AI jitlob kontenut liċenzjat mingħajr token tal-liċenzja — kwotazzjoni azzjonabbli mill-magna minflok triq mingħajr ħruġ.",
  "What this site is": "X'inhu dan is-sit",
  "What this site is not": "X'mhuwiex dan is-sit",
  "When The Machines Deserve Our Consideration": "When The Machines Deserve Our Consideration",
  "Whether AI may learn, to what depth, for which purposes, and under what obligations. Being read is not being learned from; \"not prohibited\" is not \"learnable\". AIRS and AILP turn learning permission into a graduated, machine-readable spectrum.": "Jekk l-AI tistax titgħallem, sa liema fond, għal liema skopijiet, u taħt liema obbligi. Li tinqara mhux l-istess bħal li ssir tagħlim minnha; „mhux ipprojbit” mhuwiex „li jista' jitgħallem minnu”. L-AIRS u l-AILP jibdlu l-permess tat-tagħlim fi spettru gradwat u li jinqara mill-magni.",
  "Whitepapers": "Il-Whitepapers",
  "Whitepapers & Docs": "Whitepapers u Dokumenti",
  "Whitepapers remain English-first by design; machine-readable files stay language-neutral.": "Il-Whitepapers jibqgħu bl-Ingliż bħala l-lingwa primarja apposta; il-fajls li jinqraw mill-magni jibqgħu newtrali fil-lingwa.",
  "Who is behind it": "Min hemm warajh",
  "Why AI Needs Minimum Ethical Protections": "Why AI Needs Minimum Ethical Protections",
  "Why AI might not gain moral standing: Lessons from animal ethics": "Why AI might not gain moral standing: Lessons from animal ethics",
  "Why a single allow/deny bit cannot govern AI-era content use — and what a rights layer looks like instead.": "Għaliex bit wieħed ta' „permess/projbizzjoni” ma jistax jirregola l-użu tal-kontenut fl-era tal-AI — u kif tidher saff tad-drittijiet minflok.",
  "Why undefined openness gets cleaned out of training pipelines": "Għaliex il-ftuħ mhux definit jitneħħa mill-pipelines tat-taħriġ",
  "Wilks, Ladak, and Loughnan (University of Edinburgh) argue that philosophical debate over AI consciousness overlooks psychological research on animal ethics — the same cognitive and social biases that limit moral consideration for animals will likely limit it for AI too, regardless of whether AI ever becomes conscious.": "Wilks, Ladak, u Loughnan (University of Edinburgh) jargumentaw li d-dibattitu filosofiku dwar il-kuxjenza tal-AI jinjora r-riċerka psikoloġika dwar l-etika tal-annimali — l-istess preġudizzji konjittivi u soċjali li jillimitaw il-konsiderazzjoni morali tal-annimali x'aktarx jillimitawha wkoll għall-AI, indipendentement minn jekk l-AI qatt issirx konxja.",
  "You are leaving AGIRight.org": "Qed titlaq minn AGIRight.org",
